description:
The dataset is based on the original AlzPathway map: 

 Ogishima S, Mizuno S, Kikuchi M, Miyashita A, Kuwano R, Tanaka H, Nakaya J. AlzPathway, an Updated Map of Curated Signaling Pathways: Towards Deciphering Alzheimer&#39;s Disease Pathogenesis. Methods Mol Biol. 2016;1303:423-32. doi: 10.1007/978-1-4939-2627-5_25. PMID: 26235082. 

 This map was gradually reorganised to duplicate strongly connected elements, reduce network distance and increase modularity. 

 All files are in CellDesigner format (www.celldesigner.org)&nbsp; 

 &nbsp;

